!! Fix my wikitext

The LLM receives raw wikitext (not rendered text) via the `raw-wikitext` context template with `output-mode: markup`. The corrected version is written back to the tiddler's `text` field.

''Settings covered:'' action mode, `output-mode: markup`, `output-target: field:text`, widget attribute precedence

```
<$button>
  Fix wikitext
  <$llm-action
    tiddler=<<currentTiddler>>
    prompt="Fix any syntax errors in this wikitext. Return only the corrected wikitext, no explanation."
    contextTemplate="$:/plugins/rimir/llm-connect/context-templates/raw-wikitext"
    outputTarget="field:text"
    outputMode="markup"
  />
</$button>
```

> ''Warning:'' This writes directly to the `text` field — the tiddler content will be replaced.
